"true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/we-will-destroy-the-jews-grandsons-of-hitler-and-the-mufti-meet-in-new-egyptian-movie/0000018d-8869-d0de-af8d-8c79fdc70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方在没有合法理由的情况下没收反政府抗议者的装备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-confiscate-anti-govt-protesters-equipment-without-legal-cause/0000018d-8816-d0de-af8d-8c36354a0000</link><description>在最近几周针对内塔尼亚胡政府的抗议活动中，尽管抗议者保持允许的噪音水平，但警方还是没收了扩音器、鼓和扬声器系统，导致冲突和拘留</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 12:23:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-confiscate-anti-govt-protesters-equipment-without-legal-cause/0000018d-8816-d0de-af8d-8c36354a0000</guid></item><item><title>“1948 年的创伤已被唤醒”：策展人希望将艺术带回以色列南部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bringing-art-back-to-israels-obliterated-south-the-trauma-of-1948-has-been-reawakened/0000018d-83e2-d636-adef-cfee1e2d0000</link><description>基布兹 Yad Mordechai 可能被描述为一个带有基布兹的纪念场所，而不是相反。自10月7日起，基布兹的美术馆已关闭。它的馆长现在正在寻找复兴它的方法</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 11:23:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bringing-art-back-to-israels-obliterated-south-the-trauma-of-1948-has-been-reawakened/0000018d-83e2-d636-adef-cfee1e2d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国与以色列矿业巨头丹·格特勒的斗争确凿无疑？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/a-smoking-gun-in-u-s-fight-against-israeli-mining-magnate-gertler/0000018d-7eac-d636-adef-7eee1fed0000</link><description>根据 TheMarker 获得的记录，以色列商人 Dan Gertler 显然透露了他如何规避美国因涉嫌在刚果行贿而实施的制裁，并隐瞒了一座价值 15 亿美元的铜钴矿。他的律师：“无意义的主张”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:38:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/a-smoking-gun-in-u-s-fight-against-israeli-mining-magnate-gertler/0000018d-7eac-d636-adef-7eee1fed0000</guid></item><item><title>OPSEC失败：以色列军队在加沙的阵地在网上可见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/opsec-failure-israeli-army-forces-positions-in-gaza-are-visible-online/0000018d-8813-d424-abad-9b5b70490000</link><description>在犯了无数错误之后，以色列国防军发布了明确的指导方针，以防止敏感信息泄露。但这些并没有得到执行，以色列士兵在加沙作战时不断暴露自己的行动和立场</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:29:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/opsec-failure-israeli-army-forces-positions-in-gaza-are-visible-online/0000018d-8813-d424-abad-9b5b70490000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部发现超罕见的白色彩虹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/parks-nature/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/ultra-rare-white-rainbow-spotted-in-northern-israel/0000018d-8825-d424-abad-9b7d8a920000</link><description>白色彩虹不是在雨中而是在雾中观察到。就像彩虹一样，要看到彩虹，你需要在太阳身后看着雾气</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:22:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/parks-nature/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/ultra-rare-white-rainbow-spotted-in-northern-israel/0000018d-8825-d424-abad-9b7d8a920000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡克制地与哈马斯作战直到“全面胜利”是一个幻想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-refrain-of-fighting-hamas-until-total-victory-is-a-fantasy/0000018d-87eb-df76-a1fd-cffb8ba20000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡认为自己是温斯顿·丘吉尔，不断谈论与哈马斯的战争中的“全面胜利”。他拒绝接受的是，他实际上是二战角色扮演中的绥靖者内维尔·张伯伦。以色列公众对他的信任已从根本上被打破</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:21:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-refrain-of-fighting-hamas-until-total-victory-is-a-fantasy/0000018d-87eb-df76-a1fd-cffb8ba20000</guid></item><item><title>尽管内塔尼亚胡蔑视哈马斯的提议，但他为以色列谈判敞开了大门</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/despite-netanyahus-scorn-for-hamas-proposal-he-leaves-the-door-open-for-negotiations/0000018d-87bf-df76-a1fd-cfff7c7a0000</link><description>政治消息人士认为，总理的蔑视实际上可能为继续谈判奠定了基础。美国国务卿布林肯也表示，尽管哈马斯的回应存在问题，但它“为达成协议创造了空间”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:12:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/despite-netanyahus-scorn-for-hamas-proposal-he-leaves-the-door-open-for-negotiations/0000018d-87bf-df76-a1fd-cfff7c7a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列空军预备役军官因在反政府集会上发表讲话而被停职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-air-force-suspends-reservist-officer-for-speaking-at-anti-government-rally/0000018d-8798-d424-abad-9fd8466d0000</link><description>直到哈马斯袭击后战争爆发，约拉姆·布斯基拉中校暂停了预备役职务，以抗议内塔尼亚胡政府的司法改革。战争开始时他恢复了预备役职责</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 08:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-air-force-suspends-reservist-officer-for-speaking-at-anti-government-rally/0000018d-8798-d424-abad-9fd8466d0000</guid></item><item><title>根据战时规定，以色列在没有举行听证会的情况下将巴勒斯坦被拘留者关押了八天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/using-wartime-provision-israel-holds-palestinian-detainees-for-eight-days-with-no-hearing/0000018d-8558-df76-a1fd-cff987c60000</link><description>以色列国防军和警方依赖军法中很少使用的反恐条款，导致拘留期更长。在一个案件中，七人被关押了八天，直到法官裁定他们是犯罪受害者</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 04:00:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/using-wartime-provision-israel-holds-palestinian-detainees-for-eight-days-with-no-hearing/0000018d-8558-df76-a1fd-cff987c60000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列士兵被黎巴嫩发射的火箭弹炸伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-live/blinken-hamas-response-creates-space-for-agreement-netanyahu-slams-delusional-demands/0000018d-868c-d0de-af8d-8ebc4d630000</link><description>巴勒斯坦人向约旦河西岸军队哨所开枪，被以色列国防军打