GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/netanyahu-slams-hamas-demands-as-freed-israeli-hostages-plea-him-to-avoid-moral-stain/0000018d-8501-df76-a1fd-cff1a7980000</guid></item><item><title>马克龙向 10 月 7 日遇难者家属提供了内塔尼亚胡不会提供的东西</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-07/ty-article/.highlight/macron-gave-october-7-victims-families-what-netanyahu-wont/0000018d-84e7-d424-abad-9fffc9d30000</link><description>在以色列，仍被哈马斯扣押的 100 多名人质的家人被迫乞求与内阁成员会面，并了解停火协议的最新进展，以便让他们回家</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 20:29:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-07/ty-article/.highlight/macron-gave-october-7-victims-families-what-netanyahu-wont/0000018d-84e7-d424-abad-9fffc9d30000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔加强对执法部门的控制，以色列媒体顾问接受警方讯问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-media-adviser-questioned-by-police-as-ben-gvirs-grip-on-law-enforcement-deepens/0000018d-84c1-d424-abad-9fd9cee40000</link><description>伊齐克·埃尔罗夫（Itzik Elrov）发布了一张照片，其中以色列交通部长穿着一件用沾满鲜血的爆米花制成的连衣裙。一名高级观察员表示，警方对他的讯问反映出本-格维尔的“帮派风气”对以色列警察的影响日益加深</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 19:35:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-media-adviser-questioned-by-police-as-ben-gvirs-grip-on-law-enforcement-deepens/0000018d-84c1-d424-abad-9fd9cee40000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 124 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-124/0000018d-84d9-df76-a1fd-cff94e420000</link><description>哈马斯提出 135 天停火计划 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡称哈马斯提议“妄想” ■ 由卡塔尔/埃及斡旋的新一轮人质释放协议谈判定于周四开始 ■ 沙特阿拉伯表示，如果没有独立的巴勒斯坦国，就不可能与以色列实现正常化■ 战争开始 124 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 18:41:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-124/0000018d-84d9-df76-a1fd-cff94e420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外交部夸耀巴勒斯坦 LGBTQ 庇护裁决；内政部长寻求逆转</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/foreign-ministry-boasts-lgbtq-palestinian-asylum-ruling-interior-minister-seeks-reversal/0000018d-83fb-dfd5-adff-dbfbc7a00000</link><description>特拉维夫的一名法官最近裁定，因性取向受到威胁的巴勒斯坦人可以在以色列申请庇护。外交部发布了一条推文庆祝这一裁决，然后将其删除</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 16:31:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/foreign-ministry-boasts-lgbtq-palestinian-asylum-ruling-interior-minister-seeks-reversal/0000018d-83fb-dfd5-adff-dbfbc7a00000</guid></item></channel></rss>